you'll have to deal with me.

529
00:44:39,426 --> 00:44:41,261
I can't believe this woman!

530
00:44:56,652 --> 00:45:00,364
Broccoli, I saw the article about
the casting for your husband's movie!

531
00:45:05,077 --> 00:45:06,537
