Stop bothering us!

626
00:52:37,571 --> 00:52:41,241
I told you to stop.
I said I'm not going to do it anymore!

627
00:52:44,619 --> 00:52:46,288
Why are you doing this?

628
00:52:46,371 --> 00:52:49,499
Do you want to see my family ruined?

629
00:53:35,462 --> 00:53:38,089
ORCHESTRA PERFORMANCE
